   OUR GROUP GITES IN THE PERIGORD
   Charming gite with architecture typical of the Perigord
   STUDIO APARTMENT HOLIDAY IN THE DORDOGNE
   Little farm in holiday village in the Dordogne

   4 km. from Sarlat, on a hilltop overlooking the Dordogne, discover the
   charm of our cottages built from old Périgord stone.
   This village of typical gites built from materials salvaged from old
   farms in South-West France is the ideal environment for a luxury
   holiday rental.

   Couples will love our studio apartments, families our characteristic
   houses and gatherings of friends our group gites. Enjoy the calm,
   traditional quality of life of the Dordogne.

